## Project Description

CostWise AI is an AI-powered SaaS platform designed to help HR teams, founders, and business leaders understand and optimize employee-related costs. The platform integrates workforce data and calendar information to provide intelligent insights, automate reporting, and support better hiring and resource allocation decisions.

It helps organizations reduce unnecessary spending, improve workforce planning, and make data-driven decisions through AI-generated recommendations.

---

## Approach

We started by understanding the challenges organizations face in tracking and analyzing HR expenses. Instead of relying on static spreadsheets, we designed an AI-first platform that combines employee data, schedules, and analytics into a unified dashboard.

Our approach focuses on:

* Building a secure SaaS architecture with authentication and role-based access.
* Integrating Google Calendar to understand workload and team activities.
* Using Gemini AI to generate insights and recommendations.
* Providing real-time dashboards and reports for decision-makers.
* Creating a scalable backend using TypeScript and Supabase.

The solution aims to simplify workforce cost analysis while making AI-powered insights accessible to businesses.

